headline: 3 Reasons Costco Is a Must-Buy for Long-Term Investors
summary: Costco (NASDAQ: COST) is a great example of a fantastic stock that's available at a compelling price today.  Costco is more than just another place for its millions of members to shop.  Nearly all of Costco's subscribers choose to renew their memberships each year, even when membership prices increase.
